commit_message: fix a critical bug in NW alignment

Merge pull request #4 from satoken/dev

dev container
Modify README.md about configuring with IP optimizers

Improve averaging BP matrix and linking Gurobi

* Produce the averaged BP matrix weighted by the number of sequences for
each alignment.
* Support the latest Gurobi optimizer.
Fix a bug around the sparse update
Modify the step size of the subgradient optimization
Remove m4 files for configuring boost
Fix configure setting for CPLEX detection
fix a bug around Lagrangian relaxation
implement ADAM for stochastic gradient descent.
implement AdaGrad for stochastic gradient descent
Add several files that are automatically generated to make it possible to build the products from clone/zipped files.
rename and reformat README to README.md.

fix for newer version of automake.
add .gitignore
* Option '--ipknot' sets optimized parameters for IPknot decoding.

* calculate scaling parameters for Vienna RNA package to avoid overflow
* fix a bug around bp-update1
* several modifications for Vienna RNA package 2.0.
Added tag v0.0.1 for changeset c5b69a446b78

* change the package name: dusaf -> dafs.
* change default options.
* fix the coordinates for the import of posterior probabilities.
* add a new feature: import base-pairing probabilities and alignment matching probabilities from auxiliary files.
* add an option for the iterative update for the final prediction.
* implement the iterative update of base-pairing probabilities for predicting pseudoknots.
* implement IPknot model for predicting common secondary structures with pseudoknots.
* import IPknot class from IPknot, and modify this class to be adapted.

* modify IP::solve() to get the objective value.
* modify the final common secondary structure prediction.
* implement the common secondary structure prediction for the final result.
add NeedlemanWunsch class for the new interface of decoding methods.
* add Nussinov class for the new interface of decoding methods.

* change the interface for decoding methods.
* remove PartAlign class for alignments.
* modify the iterative refinement algorithm from a randomized version to a hill climbing version.
* modify the treatment of the command line options for PCTs.

* add examples.
* add ax_func_getopt_long.m4 for use of GNU gengetopt.
* modify PCT functions.

* use GNU gengetopt to analyze command line options.
* rename new_param.{c,h} to boltzmann_param.{c,h} ,respectively.
* modify the routine for calculating distances between sequences.
* implement the sparse decoding for aligning sequences.
* implement a function to identify the alignment envelope.
* implement sparse decoding for secondary structures.
* optimize the step width for subgradient method.

* ip.cpp: suppress log messages of CPLEX. control the number of threads for CPLEX.
* enable to switch between dual decomposition and integer programming by -m option. if 0 is given, dusaf with IP will run.
